  "title": "Sales Engineer – Pipe Fabrication (CS & SS)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Business Development & Sales</strong></p><ul><li>Generate RFQs from EPC contractors, PCM contractors, industrial plants, offshore fabricators, shipyards, and system integrators</li><li>Conduct client meetings to understand piping systems, fabrication scope, and delivery requirements</li><li>Build and manage a strong pipeline of qualified RFQs</li><li>Follow up quotations proactively until order confirmation</li></ul><p><strong>Technical & Commercial Coordination</strong></p><ul><li>Review isometric drawings, P&IDs, and piping specifications</li><li>Coordinate with workshop teams on feasibility, scope, and lead time</li><li>Support pre-estimation and commercial proposal preparation</li><li>Align delivery schedules with production planning</li></ul><p><strong>Internal Coordination</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure clear scope handover after order confirmation</li><li>Support repeat orders and long-term client relationships</li><li>Act as the key interface between client and workshop</li></ul>",
